  <summary date="2019-11-07T14:06:28Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Preventing SBA Assistance from Going to China Act of 2019 

This bill prohibits the Small Business Administration from providing aid, counsel, or assistance to a small business concern that (1) is headquartered in China, or (2) has more than 25% of voting stock owned by citizens of China.</summary>
